Title: Fire Motif Zandana
Body:

Tying a bandana properly can be a nightmare (Ok, that might be a little extreme, it's more of a mild annoyance), but these handy zandana's are already made up for your wearing pleasure, shaving valuable seconds off one's getting ready time (A priceless commodity for the unorganised among us). Title: Large Dancing Skeletons Bag (Various Colours)
Body:
So what are these party hearty skeletons doing? A Barndance? A Shin-dig? A Hootenanny? (Which, by the way, is a word that doesnt get nearly enough use these days). Judging by their grinning faces they must be have a wicked time. OK, obviously a skeletons face always looks like its having a wicked time, but the point still stands. Plus I WANT one of those hats.

Lovely big roomy bag perfect for over-night stays, plus you wont get it mixed up with other, more boring bags. Result. Strong and durable, with removeable over the shoulder strap, one zippered inner pocket and one mobile phone pocket. High quality Doc Black original product. Available in a variety of colours and sizes.
